  <brief_title>Morbimortality in Older Patients Undergoing Urgent Abdominal Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Analysis of Morbimortality and Functional Status in Older Patients(&gt;65 Years Old) Undergoing Urgent Abdominal Surgery Using CRISTAL Score Modify</official_title>
  <sponsors>
